snippet.title: The Matrix Awakens: An Unreal Engine 5 Experience - The Game Awards 2021 | PS5
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10004087/

The Matrix Awakens: An Unreal Engine 5 Experience’ is here! 

Revealed at The Game Awards 2021, you can now download this tech demo for free on PlayStation®5.

Created by members of the original movie team including Lana Wachowski along with Epic Games and partners, ‘The Matrix Awakens: An Unreal Engine 5 Experience’ is a wild ride into the reality-bending universe of ‘The Matrix’ that features performances by Keanu Reeves and Carrie-Anne Moss.

Step into the world of one of the most iconic action franchises ever made. Download ‘The Matrix Awakens: An Unreal Engine 5 Experience’ now.
